    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been a total joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
