    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2017 BMW M2 (F87) featuring the N55B30 3.0L twin-scroll turbocharged inline-six. This powerplant delivers a robust torque curve managed by a precise 6-speed manual transmission with rev-matching capability. The vehicle features the Active M Differential, providing superior lateral grip and power distribution through high-load corners. The suspension architecture utilizes forged aluminum control arms to reduce unsprung mass, ensuring communicative steering feedback and chassis composure. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system inspection and fresh synthetic lubricants. This is a well-maintained, driver-spec example optimized for both longitudinal acceleration and corner-exit stability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
