    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a perfect balance of performance and daily utility, maintained with a high level of care throughout its life. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel arch are present upon close inspection\u2014typical of a well-loved car that has been driven responsibly. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple leather seats with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features, including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history; the most recent maintenance included a full synthetic oil change and a brake fluid flush. With plenty of tread left on the tires and crisp, responsive handling, this car is ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence.",
